          - rid: 107151359355650160
          - rid: 107151359355650161
          output: 'The Beholder smiles upon us! Our cleric successfully convinced
            the youth to join our ranks. With such a talented figure by our side,
            our doctrine shall breathe life upon the canvas. Through his brush, we
            shall find immortality!

            [Gained 40 Zeal, 10 Bliss & Boon]

'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650162
          output: 'Terrible news! It seems we were not the only sect attempting to
            recruit the young artist. By the time we arrived, he had already been
            indoctrinated by one of our rivals. Our followers are crestfallen at
            having lost such a grand opportunity.

            [Lost 15 Bliss]

'
